"title": "8716: dishonesty, examples of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8716",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Examples of the dishonest behaviour condemned by God.</p>\n<h2>Dishonest words condemned</h2>\n<h3>Lying</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:11\">LEV 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:13\">PSA 34:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9-Col3:10\">COL 3:9–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>False witness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:16\">EXO 20:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:20\">DEU 5:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:17-Matt19:18\">MAT 19:17–19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:19\">MRK 10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:20\">LUK 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:1\">EXO 23:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:7\">EXO 23:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:59-Matt26:60\">MAT 26:59–26:60</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:12-Acts6:14\">ACT 6:12–6:14</a></p>\n<h3>Swearing falsely</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:12\">LEV 19:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:7\">EXO 20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:33-Matt5:37\">MAT 5:33–5:37</a></p>\n<h2>Dishonest actions condemned</h2>\n<h3>Stealing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:15\">EXO 20:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:19\">DEU 5:19</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:18\">MAT 19:18</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:19\">MRK 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:20\">LUK 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:9\">ROM 13:9</a></p>\n<h3>Dishonest dealing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:1\">PRO 11:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13\">LEV 19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:13-Deut25:16\">DEU 25:13–25:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:15-Isa33:16\">ISA 33:15–33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:9-Titus2:10\">TIT 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Israel condemned for dishonest gain</h2>\n<h3>Bribery and extortion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:12-Ezek22:13\">EZK 22:12–22:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13\">JER 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:17-Jer22:19\">JER 22:17–22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:27-Ezek22:31\">EZK 22:27–22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:6-Hab2:9\">HAB 2:6–2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Cheating and dishonest scales</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4-Amos8:8\">AMO 8:4–8:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:35-Lev19:36\">LEV 19:35–19:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:10-Mic6:13\">MIC 6:10–6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:14\">MAL 1:14</a> <em>In this case, they were cheating the LORD.</em></p>\n<h2>Examples of dishonesty</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:15-Gen26:22\">GEN 26:15–26:22</a> <em>Abimelech's servants</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:29-Gen25:33\">GEN 25:29–25:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:6-Gen27:29\">GEN 27:6–27:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:31-Gen30:43\">GEN 30:31–30:43</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:21-Gen29:30\">GEN 29:21–29:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:19\">GEN 31:19</a> <em>Rachel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:36-Gen31:42\">GEN 31:36–31:42</a> <em>Laban</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:11-Josh7:26\">JOS 7:11–7:26</a> <em>Achan</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:2-1Kgs21:16\">1KI 21:2–21:16</a> <em>Ahab and Naboth's vineyard</em></p>",
